WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
Everyone ultimately wanted to have a comfortable life

00:07.000 --> 00:25.000
So we organized the people into food collectors, exchanged labour with people in the area, and managed to get some food

00:25.000 --> 00:29.000
It was not easy

00:29.000 --> 00:36.000
And it was still a hard life

00:36.000 --> 00:44.000
But it was considerably better than under the gatherer

